      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of deep space... like the scale of it all. it's just so much. and then i think about my life, my stupid little problems, and it just feels like a joke. if everything eventually just goes dark and dies anyway, what's even the point of struggling to stay here? it feels like we're just pretending that any of this matters.",
